/p>\n<p>All member <strong>Parents Association meeting Thursday 29th September 2022 @ 8pm via Zoom <\/strong>(no in person meeting and a Zoom link will be sent closer to the time). <\/p>\n<p><strong>Fireworks Night &#8211; Thursday 3rd November 202<\/strong>2 \u2013 please contact Daniel_Jude@hotmail.co.uk if you would like to be a member of the organising committee for this event. An additional request for volunteers will be made closer to the date, once the committee has decided on the stalls that will be offered.  <\/p>\n<p><strong>Christmas Fair &#8211; Saturday 26th November 2022 <\/strong>please contact Daniel_Jude@hotmail.co.uk if you would like to be a member of the organising committee for this event. An additional request for volunteers will be made closer to the date, once the committee has decided on the activities\/stalls that will be offered. Also, if you have a business or know of someone who runs a business who would be interested in hosting a stall at the event, please send me an email at the above address.<br \/>\n<em>\u00a0<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">We are always looking for new helpers and class representatives so if you can offer some time or help, no matter how small, do let us know. <\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-435 aligncenter\" style=\"color: #8d8d8d; font-family: Humanist521BT-Roman, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.69px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.beechwood.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/Firework-2-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"Firework 2\" width=\"383\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.beechwood.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/Firework-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.beechwood.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/Firework-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.beechwood.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/Firework-2-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.beechwood.org.uk\/